node.text: Been awhile since I have been in a theatre. Went to @regalmovies to see Free Guy and got too excited that I had to throw on a Regal shirt and serve up some snacks 😂😂😂 This movie was so good and even better on the big screen. Officially out today so go see it at your closest Regal Cinemas! #FreeGuyAtRegal #Ad

node.text: I truly love being on this podcast, it has and keeps teaching me so much!! Hearing some of our awesome guests talk about their struggles, overcoming obstacles, and embracing moments continue to make an impact on me. Super grateful for all the kind words on the last episode love you guys.

node.text: I’m so unbelievably proud of you dude.  Not just because you went 8 rounds with the best... Because you walked out to the song “Greatest Showman” and I would watch you tell yourself that in the mirror everyday!! You are the hardest working man I’ve ever met in my whole life, you’ve done SO much for other people and ask for ZERO in return! God has blessed you so much and I pray every single night that he gives you even more! Your heart, your work ethic and your passion will forever be number 1 congratulations to my best friend @loganpaul “The Greatest Entertainer” ❤️
